author: Atomic Shrimp
description:
I received an email asking me to make a choice about a delivery from the NHS (a delivery I *was* actually expecting).  It's a scam, but this message could appear quite plausible if you happen to be in the same situation as me.

Join the Atomic Shrimp official Discord server for FREE early access to videos! - https://discord.gg/atomicshrimp

title: Scam Awareness - NHS Routine Test Kit Delivery Scam
